OL,3,CRecord rainfall leaves 42 of farmer's
OL,4,C50 fields unusable
OL,6,FMr Chappell said he was surviving
OL,7,Fthrough government-supported green
OL,8,Ffarming schemes.
OL,10,FHe has also been hosting school trips
OL,11,Ffor extra income.
OL,13,F"I'll be open and honest. I don't know
OL,14,Fhow we will get through next year," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FHe added: "My dad got flooded once in
OL,18,F1981. Since 2000 I have lost count of
OL,19,Fthe amount of times I have been
OL,20,Fflooded."
