OL,3,CRecord rainfall leaves 42 of farmer's
OL,4,C50 fields unusable
OL,6,FThe National Farmers Union said the
OL,7,Fextreme weather was now one of the
OL,8,Fbiggest threats to UK food security.
OL,10,FRhonda Thompson, the NFU's
OL,11,FLincolnshire representative, said: "We
OL,12,Fwant to be in a position where we are
OL,13,Fproducing good quality food,
OL,14,Faffordable food for the home market.
OL,15,FOur farmers will do everything they
OL,16,Fcan to do that but they can't get on
OL,17,Fthe land."
