OL,6,FThe Government said it had opened a
OL,7,Ffarming recovery fund and was
OL,8,Fmonitoring the impact of the wet
OL,9,Fweather on the 2024 harvest.
OL,11,FA spokesperson said: "We have
OL,12,Fprotected over 900,000 acres of
OL,13,Fagricultural land from the impacts of
OL,14,Fflooding since 2015, and are investing
OL,15,F#5.6 billion to better protect
OL,16,Fcommunities from flooding and coastal
OL,17,Ferosion.
